rComments: The online videos are very helpful for all of the assignments. The final assignment takes a lot of time and effort to complete but it is interesting.

Attending each class is essential to understanding the work done in this class. The tutorial videos that are put up are a great help for the work assigned in each class. The class is a lot of fun if you like sitting in front of a computer for two and half hours.
Great class - very interesting and useful. He's a great professor (thorough, challenging, kind, helpful). I recommend this class (multimedia).

he is (somewhat) helpful in his own way, but the first midterm was ridiculous. if you want to be prepared, follow along to his videos, and then make sure you can do everything without the help of the videos. he seems like a nice guy, but very shy.
